operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>안드로이드는 elevation을 사용한다.</p>\n<p>elevation은 0부터 5까지 있으며 숫자가 커질수록 shadow가 커진다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Platform <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react-native'</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Platform을 확인하려면 Platform을 improt한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">    <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>Platform<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">select</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      ios<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        shadowColor<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"rgb(50, 50, 50)\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        shadowOpacity<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        shadowRadius<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        shadowOffset<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          height<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          width<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      android<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        elevation<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>style에 <code class=\"language-text\">...Platform.select</code>을 사용하여 ios/android에 따라 스타일을 지정해줄 수 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"cirlce\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cirlce\" aria-label=\"cirlce permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Cirlce</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">circle<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  width<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">30</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  height<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">30</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  borderRadius<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">15</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  backgroundColor<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"red\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>원 만들기, borderRadius는 항상 width와 height의 절반이어야함.</p>\n<p>그리고 상위 컨테이너에 <code class=\"language-text\">alignItems: &quot;center&quot;</code>를 지정해주면 원이 중간에 온다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"[RN]Native CSS","date":"June 03, 2020","thumbnail":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/javascript/native-css/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/javascript/redux-toolkit/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[Redux]Redux Toolkit","category":"JavaScript","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/javascript/map/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[JavaScript]map 함수","category":"JavaScript","draft":false}}}}}